did.abstract: Official records of the Stanford Chapter of Phi Beta Kappa, 1930-1970. Contents consist primarily of lists of eligible candidates, official initiation programs, financial statements and some correspondence.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition note
acqinfo.p: Administrative transfer, California Beta Chapter, Phi Beta Kappa, 1969. Administrative transfer, Academic Planning Office and President's Office, 1971. Series 3 transferred from SC1048 to SC0094, December 2016.

scopecontent.head: Description of the Collection
scopecontent.p: Official records of the Stanford Chapter of Phi Beta Kappa, 1904-1970. Contents consist primarily of lists of eligible candidates, official initiation programs, financial statements, annual dinner meeting programs, annual reports to the national headquarters, executive council minutes, and correspondence.
